  "title": "FINANCIAL SERVICES DIRECTOR",
  "description": "<p>Join the elite Private Client Division of one of Singapore’s most dynamic investment firms as we scale our presence in the high-net-worth market. In strategic partnership with global asset management titans <strong>BlackRock, Fidelity, and Schroders</strong>, and backed by a formidable private equity heritage, we deliver institutional-grade strategies to a sophisticated clientele. This Director-level mandate offers a prestigious platform to architect bespoke investment solutions, cultivate inter-generational wealth, and lead within a firm that is redefining the standard for private wealth management in Asia.<br /></p><p><strong>Preferred</strong></p><ul><li>Seasoned Private Bankers, Senior Relationship Managers, and External Asset Managers (EAM) with a proven history of serving the HNW/UHNW segment.</li><li>Advanced expertise in investment analysis, portfolio construction, and asset allocation strategies, acquired within a top-tier Private Bank, Asset Management firm, or Multi-Family Office.</li><li>Demonstrable proficiency in constructing and managing robust multi-asset class portfolios, with deep technical knowledge of equities, fixed income, and alternative investments.</li><li>Ability to synthesize and apply institutional-grade investment research from global partners to drive high-conviction client strategies.</li><li>A verifiable track record of acquiring, managing, and retaining a significant portfolio of HNW/UHNW clients. <em>Success in this role is further catalyzed by a consistent stream of qualified leads via the firm’s corporate partnerships.</em></li><li>Executive presence and the professional gravitas required to engage effectively with entrepreneurs, C-suite executives, and multi-generational families.</li><li>A commitment to delivering a \"white-glove\" service experience, characterized by outstanding communication and meticulous attention to complex client needs.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Required</strong></p><ul><li>Posses 4 MAS certificates</li><li>Singaporean Permanent Resident or Citizen only</li></ul><p><br />Send your CV to:<br />𝗽𝗵𝗶𝗹𝗶𝗽@𝘃𝗮𝗻𝗴𝘂𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗿𝗲𝗰𝗿𝘂𝗶𝘁𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁.𝗰𝗼𝗺.𝘀𝗴<br />WhatsApp: <a href=\"https://wa.me/6584520693\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://wa.me/6584520693</a></p>",
